title: WESTWORLD Season 3 Timeline Explained!
author: Think Story
comment: Had fun putting this together. I tried to make this as accurate as possible, but as you can tell sometimes the show doesn't even know exactly when things occurred.  Hope you enjoy!
Lets be honest, Westworld without westworld is okay but Westworld without ERW Dolores is not okay.
“Le why?” Hahahahahaha, that was perfect timing!
Actually "Jerry" tried to brutally murder Delores and then proceeds to trip up and smash his own skull on the side of the pool.
Who was paying Bernard motel bill? That the motel manager never evicted him for non payment.
description:
Westworld Season 3 has us travelling into the real world but also through time! In this timeline video we explain all the major events from Westworld Season 3 in chronological order.
